
Inline scripts: 
    bad code reusability
    pollution of global namespace

 |  |
 V  V

Script tags:
    Have to copy all scripts when building new web page
    lacking dependency resolution (order of script file loading)
    also, pollution of global namespace

 |  |
 V  V

IIFE (immediately invoked function expression):
    also, lacking dependency resolution

 |  |
 V  V

Common JS + Browserify: all script on one massive file. use only one script tag in html
Browserify is a script bundle tool

 |  |
 V  V

ES6 + Webpack2: export and import js files
Webpack2 is also a script bundle tool